==保护基==
*上保护基：胺与二碳酸二叔丁酯在碱（如[[碳酸氢钠|碳酸氢钠]]）的水溶液中反应，或在[[4-二甲氨基吡啶|4-二甲氨基吡啶]]（碱）的[[乙腈|乙腈]]溶液中反应。

*脱保护基：用强酸处理，如与[[三氟乙酸|三氟乙酸]]在[[二氯甲烷|二氯甲烷]]中反应或与[[盐酸|盐酸]]在[[甲醇|甲醇]]中反应。<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Robert M. Williams, Peter J. Sinclair, Duane E. DeMong, Daimo Chen, and Dongguan Zhai | prep = v80p0018 | title = 4-Morpholinecarboxylic acid, 6-oxo-2,3-diphenyl-, 1,1-dimethylethyl ester, (2S,3R)- | volume = 80 | pages = 18 | year = 2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author = E. A. Englund, H. N. Gopi, D. H. Appella | title = An Efficient Synthesis of a Probe for Protein Function: 2,3-Diaminopropionic Acid with Orthogonal Protecting Groups | journal = [[Org._Lett.|Org. Lett.]] | year = 2004 | volume = 6 | pages = 213–215 | doi = 10.1021/ol0361599}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author = D. M. Shendage, R. Fröhlich, G. Haufe | title = Highly Efficient Stereoconservative Amidation and Deamidation of α-Amino Acids | journal = [[Org._Lett.|Org. Lett.]] | year = 2004 | volume = 6 | pages = 3675–3678 | doi = 10.1021/ol048771l}}</ref>

此外，二碳酸二叔丁酯所保护的胺类也可用于其他用途，比如下图中[[6-乙酰基-1,2,3,4-四氢吡啶|6-乙酰基-1,2,3,4-四氢吡啶]]（[[Maillard反应|Maillard反应]]产物）的制取：<ref>{{cite journal en| author = Tyler J. Harrison and Gregory R. Dake | title = An Expeditious, High-Yielding Construction of the Food Aroma Compounds 6-Acetyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydropyridine and 2-Acetyl-1-pyrroline | journal = [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]] | year = 2005 | volume = 70 | issue = 26 | pages = 10872–10874 | doi = 10.1021/jo051940a}}</ref>

